⍝ ExpandAxis.tc
⍝ ═════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: LO Boolean; X∊⍳⍴⍴B
      ⍝ inv: (⍴Z)[,X] ←→ ⍴,LO   (expanded axis length = ⍴LO)
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ⍴⍴B
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      LO ← 2∣|⎕RVAL 1 (,5) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      LO[1+3∣|⎕RVAL 0] ← 1                   ⍝ ensure at least one 1
      Z ← LO\[1]B
      (1↑⍴Z) ≡ ⍴,LO
1
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ⍴⍴B
1
